These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, cabbage
1. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Food   | broccoli | cabbage |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, horror
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | horror |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, funk
1. the fan of soul is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | funk | soul |

 #################################

 
